upcoming.name: What can we learn from CODELABS?
upcoming.description:
[Apèsi - Overview]

Nou tout konnen mache travay la nan lemonnantye ap chanje vit e l ap grandi. Anpil nouvo djòb ap parèt. Parapò ak chanjman sa yo, ki kote Ayiti kanpe? Ki jan CODELABS kapab yon gwo zouti pou n kòmanse prepare n fas ak chanjman sa yo? Kesyon sa yo e plis toujou pral diskite nan evènman sa a!
--
We all know that the labor market is fastly changing and growing. Lots of new jobs are emerging. Regarding those changes, where does Haiti stand for? How CODELABS could be a great tool to prepare for these changes? These and many other questions will be discussed at this event!

Adrès / Address

Bizoton 53, Carrefour, Auditorium College Jn Baptiste Lappé
